  "keyFeatures": [
    "Role-based access control with Admin, Customer, and Laundrer roles",
    "Real-time service queue with waiting time algorithm based on active laundrers",
    "Multi-currency financial engine (USD and Venezuelan Bolívares) with automatic BCV exchange rate fetching",
    "Automated daily payroll calculation via commission pool system",
    "Customer self-service portal: reservations, order tracking, and purchase history",
    "Automated reservation-to-queue pipeline via cron jobs",
    "Inventory management with automatic stock deduction on sales",
    "Admin KPI dashboard with top customers, revenue metrics, and balance tracking",
    "Docker-based deployment with PostgreSQL 15 and Prisma ORM",
    "Weather-based DSS (Decision Support System) for service recommendations"
  ],
